<section class="section s5-process">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2 class="s5-process__heading">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>

    <div class="s5-process__steps">

      <div class="s5-process__step">
        <h3 class="s5-process__step-title">Personalized Consultation</h3>
        <p class="s5-process__step-body">Before your NAD+ IV therapy session, you'll have a brief consultation with our team to discuss your health goals and ensure NAD+ IV therapy is right for you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-process__step">
        <h3 class="s5-process__step-title">Relax and Recharge</h3>
        <p class="s5-process__step-body">Sit back in one of our comfortable therapy chairs as the NAD+ solution is administered slowly over 2-4 hours. Many clients read, work, or simply relax.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-process__step">
        <h3 class="s5-process__step-title">Feel the Benefits</h3>
        <p class="s5-process__step-body">NAD+ therapy benefits are often cumulative. While some feel an immediate boost in clarity and energy, the most profound anti-aging and restorative effects build over a series of sessions.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s5-process__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .s5-process__steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s5-process__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-cta);
  }

  .s5-process__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s5-process__step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .s5-process__step {
      padding: var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
